					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="1144" height="1430" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/image-208.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/image-208.png?w=1144&amp;ssl=1 1144w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/image-208.png?resize=768%2C960&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/image-208.png?resize=117%2C146&amp;ssl=1 117w" sizes="(max-width: 1144px) 100vw, 1144px" /></p>
