					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="1168" height="1402" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image-348.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image-348.png?w=1168&amp;ssl=1 1168w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image-348.png?resize=768%2C922&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/image-348.png?resize=122%2C146&amp;ssl=1 122w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1168px) 100vw, 1168px" /></p>
<p>近日，前白宮首席策略師史蒂夫·班農爆出了震驚全球的消息：美國將與新中國聯邦合作，成立一個專門針對中共威脅的情報 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/03/30/%e6%83%85%e5%a0%b1%e6%88%b0%e5%8d%87%e7%b4%9a%ef%bc%9a%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e8%81%af%e6%89%8b%e6%96%b0%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e8%81%af%e9%82%a6%e8%a8%ad%e3%80%8cb%e9%9a%8a%e3%80%8d%e7%9b%b4%e6%93%8a%e4%b8%ad/">情報戰升級：美國聯手新中國聯邦設「B隊」直擊中共</a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
