		<title>最新民調出爐！台南市民憂心電力不足 逾七成：應提高台南電力自給率</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2024/10/26/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b0%91%e8%aa%bf%e5%87%ba%e7%88%90%ef%bc%81%e5%8f%b0%e5%8d%97%e5%b8%82%e6%b0%91%e6%86%82%e5%bf%83%e9%9b%bb%e5%8a%9b%e4%b8%8d%e8%b6%b3-%e9%80%be%e4%b8%83%e6%88%90%ef%bc%9a%e6%87%89/</link>
					<comments>https://firenews.com.tw/2024/10/26/%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e6%b0%91%e8%aa%bf%e5%87%ba%e7%88%90%ef%bc%81%e5%8f%b0%e5%8d%97%e5%b8%82%e6%b0%91%e6%86%82%e5%bf%83%e9%9b%bb%e5%8a%9b%e4%b8%8d%e8%b6%b3-%e9%80%be%e4%b8%83%e6%88%90%ef%bc%9a%e6%87%89/#respond</comments>
		
